data.description: This open layout in the Deer Creek school district features a beautiful kitchen with built-in stainless appliances and large island with granite countertop and pendant lighting. Enjoy cozy meals by the fire with the dining room's very own fireplace. The primary suite downstairs and two bedrooms upstairs makes for some privacy while the downstairs guest room could be used as a secondary office, if needed. Upstairs game room could also be used as a kids play area or even a second living room. This house sits on almost an acre with a Greenbelt right in your backyard. Back of the property extends to the end of the tree line with its own fence.
